refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringfalseget_parent_class objectstringobject_or_class
检索对象或者类的父级类名。

&reftitle.parameters;




   object_or_class



     检查的对象或者类名。如果是从对象内的方法中调用此函数，则此参数可选。

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.0.0

     object_or_class 参数现在仅接受对象或者有效的类名。

  &reftitle.examples;



    使用 get_parent_class


<?php

class Dad {
    function __construct()
    {
    // implements some logic
    }
}

class Child extends Dad {
    function __construct()
    {
        echo "I'm " , get_parent_class($this) , "'s son\n";
    }
}

class Child2 extends Dad {
    function __construct()
    {
        echo "I'm " , get_parent_class('child2') , "'s son too\n";
    }
}

$foo = new child();
$bar = new child2();

?>


    &example.outputs;


I'm Dad's son
I'm Dad's son too
